title: still did not receive my doom bots icon
body: I still have not received my doom bots icon from winning a doom bots game. Its been well over a week and i was wondering if the game of doom bots i played counted or not.

replies.body: The icons are being sent out to a lot of players, so it's going to be a bit.  We aim to finish sending them out by the 17th, per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page.  Hang tight!
